B with CMB lensing is measured over a wider area while restricting the\nmore challenging CIB auto-spectrum measurement to the cleanest 5% of the sky.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2020 17:52:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-19"}
