 the F-theory $\\alpha'$ corrections to gauge threshold\ncorrections of the dual heterotic theory we predict how the masses of this\ntower must be renormalised in order for the Weak Gravity Conjecture to hold at\nthe quantum level.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2020 18:07:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Nov 2020 16:57:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2021 19:11:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-14"}
