ive and 50 Ohm termination cases,\nand their performances have been compared with EQS HBC for similar sized\ndevices, over varying distance between TX and RX. The resulting report presents\nthe first fundamental understanding towards M-HBC operation and its contrast\nwith EQS HBC, aiding HBC device designers to make educated design decisions,\ndepending on mode of applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2020 22:21:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-03"}
