onstruct an approximate $3$-design that only involves such $2$-qubit\ntransvections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2020 22:27:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 May 2021 20:55:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-27"}
