les us to estimate that at least 1.22 wt% of the hydrogen is present in the\nform of organics. This richness in organics strengthens the connection between\nCeres and cometary materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 31 Oct 2020 14:00:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-03"}
